data.description: Priced to sell. 3/2 duplex with its private driveway and backyard. Rapidly appreciating West Side area and so many development projects in progress in West Side & along the Niagara St. The owner has spent more than $20K for the updates, which include concrete driveway, bathroom remodel, siding the rear part of the house, windows, hot water tank, kitchen and many other miscellaneous items. Long-term tenant would like to stay. Rent was just raised to $800.00 Showings start immediately with 24-hour notice. Lower apt is only for the second showing due to tenants’ work schedule. This won't last long in the market.
